Package org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.ui.menu

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddSelectionToPlaylistMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the addition of a songs to a playlist.
    ImportDirectoryMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of import a directory into the songs library of SongsManager.
    ImportFilesMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of import one or more files into the songs library of SongsManager.
    MenuItemAction
    Represents a MenuItem that embeds an action an optionally allow to use through a shortcut (accelerator).
    PauseResumeSongMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of pause/resume the song that is currently played by SongPlayer.
    PlayNextSongMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of play the next song of SongPlayer.
    PlayPrevSongMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of play the previous song of SongPlayer.
    PlaySongMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of play the queue of songs provided by PlayableSongQueueProvider.
    QuitMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of quit the application.
    RemoveAllSongsFromLibraryMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of remove every song from a list of songs provided by a SongListProvider.
    RemovePlaylistMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of remove a playlist provided by PlaylistProvider from the the playlists of PlaylistsManager.
    RemoveSelectedSongsFromLibraryMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of remove the selected songs provided by SongSelectionProvider from a list of songs provided by a SongListProvider.
    ViewSongMenuItemAction
    MenuItemAction that performs the action of invoke SongViewer.viewSong(Song) on a song provided by SongProvider.
